{"type":"freeform","cover":{"titleText":"","subTitleText":"","presenterText":"","dateText":"","logos":[]},"section":{"sectionText":"","smallerSectionText":""},"freeform":{"content":[[{"type":"text","span":3,"markdown":"Pour les enfants de moins de 5 ans dans les programmes de nutrition, les volumes atteignent deux pics notables, autour de novembre 2023 et début 2024, suivis d’une baisse en 2025.

Le nombre d’enfants de 6 à 59 mois ayant reçu deux doses de vitamine A reste plus stable.

Ces tendances suggèrent des campagnes ou des activités ponctuelles influençant les volumes rapportés, tandis que la prestation régulière de services demeure plus constante pour la supplémentation en vitamine A.","stretch":true,"fillArea":true,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"grey","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":false,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false},{"type":"figure","stretch":true,"fillArea":false,"textSize":1,"textBackground":"none","placeholderInvisible":false,"placeholderStretch":true,"placeholderHeight":50,"useFigureAdditionalScale":true,"figureAdditionalScale":1,"imgHeight":300,"imgFit":"inside","imgStretch":true,"hideFigureCaption":false,"hideFigureSubCaption":false,"hideFigureFootnote":false,"presentationObjectInReportInfo":{"id":"e1ca7b9f-6458-4da5-b781-fde582fd6203","moduleId":"m003","isDefault":false,"selectedReplicantValue":""}}]],"useHeader":true,"headerText":"Tendances en soins de nutrition","useFooter":false,"footerText":""}}

